 * - `.testimonial-avatar-none`     - Hide avatar completely
 * - `.testimonial-avatar-placeholder` - Show gradient placeholder
 * - `.testimonial-avatar-icon`     - Show user icon SVG
 * - `.testimonial-avatar-initials` - Show first/last name initials
 * 
 * STAR RATING CLASSES:
 * --------------------
 * - `.testimonial-rating`          - Container for star ratings (required)
 * - `.testimonial-rating-show`     - Show ratings by default (override hidden state)
 * - `.testimonial-rating-hide`     - Hide ratings (default state)
 * 
 * TESTIMONIAL STRUCTURE CLASSES:
 * -------------------------------
 * - `.testimonial-card`            - Main testimonial container (required for toggles)
 * - `.testimonial-avatar`          - Avatar container (required for avatar toggles)
 * - `.testimonial-content`         - Testimonial text content area
 * - `.testimonial-author`          - Author name and job container
 * 
 * DATA ATTRIBUTES (Required for JavaScript features):
 * ---------------------------------------------------
 * - `data-name="John Doe"`         - Person's full name (for initials, required)
 * - `data-image-src="url"`         - Profile image URL (for avatar toggles)
 * - `data-image-alt="alt text"`    - Image alt text (accessibility)
 * - `data-rating="5"`               - Star rating 1-5 (for star display)
 * 
 * ============================================================================
 * HOW TO USE MODULAR CLASSES
 * ============================================================================
 * 
