 * - `longTestimonials`: Detailed, story-driven testimonials (Style 9 - Long Form)
 * - `videoTestimonials`: Video testimonials with video metadata
 * 
 * ============================================================================
 * CUSTOMIZING TESTIMONIAL STYLES
 * ============================================================================
 * 
 * 1. COPY A STYLE SECTION:
 *    - Find the style you like (e.g., Style 3: Featured + Grid)
 *    - Copy the entire `<section>` block
 *    - Paste it into your own page
 * 
