 *    - Change grid columns: `lg:grid-cols-3` → `lg:grid-cols-2` or `lg:grid-cols-4`
 *    - Modify spacing: `gap-6` → `gap-4` or `gap-8`
 *    - Adjust padding: `p-6` → `p-4` or `p-8`
 * 
