 *    - Small: `h-10 w-10` (40px)
 *    - Medium: `h-12 w-12` (48px)
 *    - Large: `h-16 w-16` (64px)
 *    - Extra Large: `h-20 w-20` (80px)
 *    - Huge: `h-32 w-32` (128px)
 * 
 * ============================================================================
 * AVATAR TOGGLE FUNCTIONALITY
 * ============================================================================
 * 
 * HOW IT WORKS:
 * -------------
 * The avatar toggle buttons dynamically change avatar display modes across sections.
 * 
 * REQUIREMENTS:
 * - Avatar container must have class: `.testimonial-avatar`
 * - Testimonial card must have: `data-name`, `data-image-src`, `data-image-alt`
 * - Toggle buttons must have: `class="avatar-toggle-btn"`, `data-section`, `data-mode`
 * 
 * DISPLAY MODES:
 * - image: Shows actual profile picture
 * - none: Hides avatar completely (removes from layout)
 * - placeholder: Shows gradient placeholder box
 * - icon: Shows user icon SVG
 * - initials: Shows first and last name initials (e.g., "JD" for "John Doe")
 * 
 * TO ADD TOGGLE BUTTONS TO YOUR PAGE:
 * -----------------------------------
 * 
 * <div class="mb-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2">
 *   <button type="button" 
 *           class="avatar-toggle-btn active px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-primary text-white" 
 *           data-mode="image" 
 *           data-section="your-section-id">
 *     Photo
 *   </button>
 *   <button type="button" 
 *           class="avatar-toggle-btn px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700" 
 *           data-mode="none" 
 *           data-section="your-section-id">
 *     None
 *   </button>
 *   <!-- Add more modes: placeholder, icon, initials -->
 * </div>
 * 
 * WRAP YOUR TESTIMONIALS:
 * -----------------------
 * 
 * <div class="testimonial-section" data-section="your-section-id">
 *   <!-- Your testimonials here -->
 * </div>
 * 
 * ============================================================================
 * STAR RATING FUNCTIONALITY
 * ============================================================================
 * 
 * HOW IT WORKS:
 * -------------
 * Star ratings can be toggled globally or shown/hidden per testimonial.
 * 
 * ADDING RATINGS TO A TESTIMONIAL:
 * ---------------------------------
 * 
 * 1. Add rating to data:
 *    { testimonial: '...', name: '...', rating: 5 }
 * 
 * 2. Add HTML (copy this pattern):
 * 
 *    {testimonial.rating && (
 *      <div class="testimonial-rating mb-4" data-rating={testimonial.rating} style="display: none;">
 *        <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
 *          {[0, 1, 2, 3, 4].map((i) => (
 *            <svg 
 *              key={i}
 *              class={`w-4 h-4 ${i < testimonial.rating ? 'text-yellow-400 fill-current' : 'text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600'}`}
 *              fill={i < testimonial.rating ? 'currentColor' : 'none'}
 *              stroke="currentColor"
 *              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
 *            >
 *              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z" />
 *            </svg>
 *          ))}
 *        </div>
 *      </div>
 *    )}
 * 
 * CUSTOMIZATION:
 * --------------
 * - Star color: Change `text-yellow-400` to `text-primary`, `text-orange-400`, etc.
 * - Star size: Change `w-4 h-4` to `w-5 h-5` (larger) or `w-3 h-3` (smaller)
 * - Always visible: Remove `style="display: none;"` or add `testimonial-rating-show` class
 * - Always hidden: Add `testimonial-rating-hide` class
 * 
 * GLOBAL TOGGLE:
 * --------------
 * The "Show Ratings" button at the top toggles ALL ratings with class `.testimonial-rating`
 * (except those with `testimonial-rating-show` class which are always visible)
 * 
 * ============================================================================
 * USING TESTIMONIALS ON OTHER PAGES
 * ============================================================================
 * 
