 *   </div>
 *   
 *   <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
 *     <div class="testimonial-avatar testimonial-avatar-image h-12 w-12 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
 *       <img src="/avatar.jpg" alt="John Doe" class="h-12 w-12 object-cover" />
 *     </div>
 *     <div class="testimonial-author">
 *       <p class="font-semibold">John Doe</p>
 *       <p class="text-sm text-muted">CEO</p>
 *     </div>
 *   </div>
 * </div>
 * 
 * ============================================================================
 * REMOVING STYLES YOU DON'T NEED
 * ============================================================================
 * 
 * 1. Delete the entire `<section id="style-X">` block
 * 2. Remove the corresponding link from the navigation index
 * 3. Remove the testimonial data arrays if they're no longer used
 * 
 * ============================================================================
 * TROUBLESHOOTING
 * ============================================================================
 * 
 * AVATAR TOGGLES NOT WORKING:
 * - Ensure avatar has class `.testimonial-avatar`
 * - Check that card has `data-name`, `data-image-src` attributes
 * - Verify toggle buttons have `data-section` matching section ID
 * - Check browser console for JavaScript errors
 * 
 * STAR RATINGS NOT SHOWING:
 * - Ensure rating div has class `.testimonial-rating`
 * - Check that testimonial data has `rating: 5` property
 * - Verify `data-rating` attribute matches the rating value
 * - Click "Show Ratings" button to toggle visibility
 * 
 * STYLES NOT APPLYING:
 * - Check that Tailwind CSS is properly configured
 * - Verify class names are spelled correctly
 * - Ensure responsive prefixes (md:, lg:) are used correctly
 * 
 * ============================================================================
 * ADVANCED CUSTOMIZATION
 * ============================================================================
 * 
 * CUSTOM AVATAR SIZES:
 * --------------------
 * Create your own size by combining height/width classes:
 * - `h-14 w-14` (56px)
 * - `h-24 w-24` (96px)
 * - Any Tailwind size class works
 * 
 * CUSTOM STAR COLORS:
 * ------------------
 * Use any Tailwind color:
 * - `text-primary` (your brand color)
 * - `text-orange-400` (orange stars)
 * - `text-pink-400` (pink stars)
 * - `text-blue-400` (blue stars)
 * 
 * CUSTOM LAYOUTS:
 * --------------
 * Mix and match grid classes:
 * - `grid-cols-1` (single column)
 * - `grid-cols-2` (two columns)
 * - `grid-cols-3` (three columns)
 * - `grid-cols-4` (four columns)
 * - Use responsive: `sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4`
 * 
 * ============================================================================
